      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tuxiaoshu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1754137-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tuxiaoshu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">ztl</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-05-13"
      class="main-meta">2017-05-13 17:31:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8537724_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  首先，资本主义是必然要出现，无论有没有韦伯所谓的新教伦理，还是有没有13世纪到18世纪欧洲几个国家奢侈消费的潮流。就像是一个人必然要死，至于是病死、出车祸撞死还是自杀，都不过是一种历史元素，而不是一种理论上的逻辑元素。这就是桑巴特和韦伯的观点的定位。   这样，桑...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8537724_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8537724_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
